column5: So a friend of mine made me aware of this. It is a CTV News article of a guy catching a 3 eyed walleye being caught on Nipissing a few weeks ago.   http://m.theglobeandmail.com/technology/technology-video/video-ontario-ice-fisherman-catches-fish-with-third-eye-in-its-forehead/article16562719/?service=mobile  here is CBC report on it, if the other link doesn't work.  http://www.cbc.ca/player/Radio/Local+Shows/Ontario/Points+North/ID/2432997569/  There are also pictures if you google it
